WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

01:06.540 --> 01:07.220
[The Eternal Fragrance]

01:07.220 --> 01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 10]

01:15.910 --> 01:16.890
Riyan!

01:18.750 --> 01:20.090
Riyan!

01:28.000 --> 01:30.170
Let them go!

01:31.160 --> 01:32.530
If you want spirit energy, take mine.

01:34.520 --> 01:36.500
Use this useless disciple as a vessel

01:36.750 --> 01:38.450
to get all the fox spirit's cultivation,

01:38.600 --> 01:40.170
and I'll be the strongest in the Central Plains.

01:41.360 --> 01:43.140
Then I won't need your little spirit energy.

01:44.160 --> 01:44.860
Beast!

01:46.720 --> 01:47.810
He's your disciple!

01:48.110 --> 01:50.500
When his meridians shattered, and his life faded,

01:50.720 --> 01:52.450
I kept him alive with my spirit energy.

01:53.030 --> 01:56.060
Today, he is repaying my kindness.

01:56.830 --> 01:58.530
Once I've got all his spirit energy,

01:59.390 --> 02:01.980
I'll send you two to death.

02:02.880 --> 02:05.810
This tomboy won't escape, either.

02:45.550 --> 02:46.130
Shanhua.

03:20.800 --> 03:23.900
Shanhua, it's Xiuyuan.

03:25.110 --> 03:27.300
Xiuyuan.

03:30.550 --> 03:32.740
My name is Lu Shanhua, your guard.

03:33.520 --> 03:34.410
From this day forward,

03:35.040 --> 03:37.410
I'll protect you with my life.

03:45.670 --> 03:46.300
Continue.

03:55.240 --> 03:56.340
We've agreed

03:57.200 --> 03:58.300
to roam the world together,

03:58.640 --> 03:59.570
find a secluded place,

04:00.080 --> 04:01.650
and never live as fugitives again.

04:18.320 --> 04:18.940
Shanhua.

04:22.150 --> 04:22.770
Shanhua.

04:24.120 --> 04:27.100
Xiuyuan, kill me.

04:27.680 --> 04:29.740
Hurry, end my life.

04:30.390 --> 04:34.570
Shanhua, don't give up. I'll save you.

05:29.390 --> 05:30.980
Finally, I wield

05:32.000 --> 05:35.130
the fox spirit's power.

05:57.080 --> 05:58.100
The demonic energy!

06:00.200 --> 06:01.300
Who are you?

06:44.320 --> 06:45.540
Where are my spirit roots?

06:49.270 --> 06:51.130
Demon!

06:51.910 --> 06:55.540
Demon!

07:09.150 --> 07:09.810
Shanhua,

07:11.230 --> 07:11.770
wake up.

07:13.470 --> 07:14.450
It's Xiuyuan.

07:16.230 --> 07:17.300
All has come to an end.

07:19.350 --> 07:20.450
It's over.

07:28.390 --> 07:29.010
Shanhua.

07:31.960 --> 07:34.060
Shanhua, wake up.

07:37.440 --> 07:38.250
Shanhua.

07:43.120 --> 07:43.660
Shanhua.

07:43.680 --> 07:44.940
Kill me.

07:46.000 --> 07:46.980
Kill me.

07:47.960 --> 07:49.620
Kill me.

07:54.000 --> 07:56.250
Just kill me!

08:02.120 --> 08:05.180
Hurry up and do it!

08:17.830 --> 08:20.300
Kill me!

09:08.590 --> 09:09.570
Xiuyuan,

09:12.110 --> 09:12.940
take care.

09:56.440 --> 09:57.090
Lifei!

10:00.110 --> 10:00.690
Lifei!

10:01.510 --> 10:04.420
Lifei, come on, get up.

10:07.440 --> 10:08.210
Are you alright?

10:09.200 --> 10:09.900
I'm fine.

10:15.400 --> 10:16.570
I'll kill him!

10:19.080 --> 10:19.900
Take me away.

10:25.080 --> 10:25.660
Alright.

11:09.560 --> 11:12.690
Master, why can't I make friends?

11:14.080 --> 11:15.570
Countless wicked folk are out in the world.

11:15.830 --> 11:17.380
What if you befriend someone untrustworthy

11:17.630 --> 11:18.850
and lose your life?

11:22.680 --> 11:23.610
Master,

11:25.510 --> 11:26.970
you really are a jinx.

11:31.820 --> 11:33.180
You should never have saved him back then.

11:35.230 --> 11:36.850
Blame my soft-hearted nature.

11:38.100 --> 11:40.260
From now on, stay far away from him.

11:40.820 --> 11:41.970
Cut all ties with him.

11:46.630 --> 11:48.690
Learn your lesson after suffering such losses.

11:52.710 --> 11:54.300
I shall return to nurture my primordial spirit.

11:54.750 --> 11:55.690
Take care of yourself.

11:59.060 --> 12:00.260
He hurt you so badly,

12:01.590 --> 12:03.060
yet you risked everything to save me.

12:03.230 --> 12:04.940
Do you think I saved you?

12:07.420 --> 12:09.850
Enough of this. Stay sharp from now on,

12:10.110 --> 12:11.180
and protect yourself.

12:11.470 --> 12:12.450
Hurry back to the academy.

12:12.680 --> 12:13.260
Understood.

12:35.040 --> 12:35.660
Lifei!

12:37.540 --> 12:39.300
Lifei!

12:42.040 --> 12:42.850
I knew I'd find you here.

12:44.040 --> 12:45.210
Why did you leave without a word?

12:46.040 --> 12:46.660
Nothing.

12:48.320 --> 12:49.570
Just wanted to take a look back here.

12:52.200 --> 12:55.180
Blame me for being set on recruiting Lei Xiuyuan,

12:56.320 --> 12:57.690
and I nearly got you killed.

13:00.400 --> 13:01.380
I was so foolish that I

13:03.440 --> 13:05.300
even planned to help him save Lu.

13:07.750 --> 13:08.570
Honestly…

13:09.510 --> 13:10.540
He hid his true identity so deeply

13:12.920 --> 13:14.300
and even risked his life.

13:14.540 --> 13:15.660
We'd never see through it.

13:17.590 --> 13:18.970
After all my schemes and posturing,

13:20.040 --> 13:21.540
I never expected to be tricked.

13:22.960 --> 13:26.210
It's fine. We're even on favors and debts. Strangers from now on.

13:27.200 --> 13:28.060
Clean and simple.

13:29.280 --> 13:29.810
Lifei,

13:34.710 --> 13:37.450
would you go to the Yue State with me?

13:40.110 --> 13:41.020
Time to return to the academy.

13:41.830 --> 13:42.940
I need to find my master

13:43.710 --> 13:44.810
and stay alive.

13:46.470 --> 13:47.610
We've been away for too long.

14:12.040 --> 14:14.900
Lifei, you've been back for days.

14:15.440 --> 14:16.940
Why only practice without saying a word?

14:17.750 --> 14:18.540
Where's Xiuyuan?

14:28.230 --> 14:30.300
Lifei, have you seen Xiuyuan?

14:30.710 --> 14:31.810
You went to Xingzheng Hall together.

14:32.040 --> 14:33.330
I asked Tongzhou, but he hasn't seen him.

14:33.870 --> 14:34.970
Could anything go wrong with him?

14:36.830 --> 14:37.490
Ask someone else.

14:39.710 --> 14:40.260
Wait.

14:42.590 --> 14:43.260
Lifei.

14:56.830 --> 14:57.490
Lifei.

14:59.590 --> 15:00.490
What are you doing back here?

15:04.870 --> 15:05.810
I need to talk to you.

15:06.470 --> 15:09.210
We have nothing to say. Leave.

15:15.470 --> 15:16.210
Sorry.

15:18.100 --> 15:19.140
I must save Shanhua.

15:19.470 --> 15:20.380
No need to apologize.

15:22.750 --> 15:25.260
I was blind and foolish.

15:27.940 --> 15:31.610
I knew you held other plans, yet I trusted you.

15:36.350 --> 15:37.730
Quit putting on that miserable act.

15:38.940 --> 15:43.090
Henceforth, we are strangers,

15:46.180 --> 15:47.060
without any ties between us.

15:53.300 --> 15:54.020
Lei Xiuyuan.

16:03.710 --> 16:04.380
Come with me.

16:23.750 --> 16:24.450
I'm sorry.

16:24.940 --> 16:27.660
What good are empty apologies?

16:28.460 --> 16:30.970
We treated you with sincerity, yet you tricked us.

16:31.700 --> 16:32.850
If Zhenyunzi had succeeded,

16:33.340 --> 16:34.450
what would have become of Lifei?

16:34.630 --> 16:35.140
What about me?

16:35.180 --> 16:36.420
And what about Xuanshanzi?

16:41.180 --> 16:41.850
Let's fight!

16:46.470 --> 16:50.330
Don't go too far in duels. You might kill each other.

16:50.700 --> 16:52.060
Talk this through calmly, alright?

16:53.220 --> 16:55.380
If you lose control again, you'll be expelled from the academy.

16:57.110 --> 17:00.380
Xiuyuan, you're careful. My chicken has grown up.

17:00.420 --> 17:02.180
I need someone to build a coop for it.

17:02.510 --> 17:04.090
Could you help me? Let's go.

17:07.630 --> 17:08.340
Go.

17:10.420 --> 17:11.140
Let's go.

17:54.470 --> 17:55.100
Come out.

18:06.070 --> 18:07.100
If you can't stand the sight of me,

18:08.030 --> 18:11.140
pretend I'm not here at all.

18:12.460 --> 18:13.620
Do you think trailing after me

18:14.070 --> 18:15.140
will make me forgive you?

18:18.460 --> 18:19.530
I don't ask for your forgiveness.

18:23.180 --> 18:24.050
I only want to make amends.

18:24.420 --> 18:25.140
Make amends?

18:29.310 --> 18:30.660
Suppose you get me killed,

18:31.030 --> 18:32.450
would you cry at my grave?

18:34.790 --> 18:37.970
I'm sorry. I thought, as I did it myself,

18:38.510 --> 18:39.580
I wouldn't hurt you so badly.

18:41.030 --> 18:42.210
But I never expected Zhenyunzi's scheme.

18:44.270 --> 18:45.530
You thought he only wanted Riyan

18:46.550 --> 18:47.900
and that you could protect me.

18:48.360 --> 18:49.420
Who could you protect?

18:55.220 --> 18:56.490
Lu is important to you, I know.

18:56.980 --> 18:58.490
But Riyan also means a lot to me.

18:59.940 --> 19:01.530
Why did you use me and sacrifice Riyan?

19:02.030 --> 19:03.420
Why deceive me over and over?

19:08.940 --> 19:09.820
You planned every step.

19:11.120 --> 19:12.620
You risked yourself at Hongyang Hall

19:13.550 --> 19:15.340
and Kept Zong Quan from hurting me.

19:16.360 --> 19:17.900
What a clever pity play.

19:21.470 --> 19:22.380
You're ruthless

19:23.620 --> 19:26.210
enough to be cruel to yourself and me.

19:27.510 --> 19:28.970
I've got nothing to compare to that.

19:33.980 --> 19:35.010
What's done is done.

19:36.270 --> 19:38.210
All these gestures to make it up to me now

19:38.750 --> 19:40.010
are to make yourself feel better.

19:41.310 --> 19:42.290
I'll never trust you again.

19:43.790 --> 19:45.010
At least let me do one thing for you.

19:45.030 --> 19:45.730
No need.

19:47.550 --> 19:48.620
Save yourself the embarrassment.

20:20.750 --> 20:21.420
Mr. Mo,

20:23.840 --> 20:25.730
please break the Fragrance Bond.

20:28.030 --> 20:28.730
Why?

20:31.880 --> 20:33.490
All gatherings must come to an end.

20:34.440 --> 20:35.490
We're bound to part sooner or later.

20:37.070 --> 20:38.620
No point keeping it active anymore.

20:42.880 --> 20:43.900
Life is fleeting.

20:45.270 --> 20:48.250
The encounters and companions of our youth

20:48.600 --> 20:49.620
are all precious treasures.

20:51.270 --> 20:53.580
Wouldn't it be a pity to cast them aside easily?

21:00.600 --> 21:03.540
♪It's me, blinded by longing♪

21:03.700 --> 21:06.680
♪Every glance lands on you♪

21:07.080 --> 21:12.200
♪Fire and water clash, yet we cling inseparably♪

21:12.800 --> 21:15.160
♪Lotus broken, threads still bind us♪

21:15.640 --> 21:18.920
♪My heart calm till you stir storms and rain♪

21:19.280 --> 21:22.840
♪You are my destined rival♪

21:23.720 --> 21:26.320
♪Winters pass, springs come; bound for lifetimes♪

21:26.480 --> 21:28.920
♪Fate ties me to you♪

21:29.480 --> 21:32.160
♪Mountains, rivers, lakes and seas♪

21:32.480 --> 21:35.040
♪I follow no one but you♪

21:35.600 --> 21:38.280
♪Bitterness brews sweet bliss♪

21:38.760 --> 21:41.280
♪Drained in one sip♪

21:41.720 --> 21:46.640
♪Love and feud balance out, I'm yours alone♪

21:47.200 --> 21:49.600
♪Fated foes, fate plays tricks♪

21:49.960 --> 21:52.320
♪You complete my five elements♪

21:53.000 --> 21:55.600
♪Burning love, unbridled hatred♪

21:55.880 --> 21:58.560
♪They suit each other well♪

21:58.920 --> 22:05.120
♪If you don't leave, I'll never abandon you♪

22:05.520 --> 22:09.360
♪We'll dwell in mortal dust♪

22:09.800 --> 22:14.360
♪Stay side by side till the end♪

22:23.070 --> 22:26.050
Break it off. All is hollow affection.

22:26.880 --> 22:27.940
Nothing is worth clinging to.

22:28.680 --> 22:29.860
What exactly happened?

22:36.750 --> 22:39.860
Nothing. I've just seen the truth.

22:42.640 --> 22:43.290
Fine.

22:44.440 --> 22:47.050
But you three must stand united to break it.

22:47.680 --> 22:49.940
Any missteps will hurt your spirit meridians.

22:52.070 --> 22:54.180
Discuss with the other two and come to me.

23:10.230 --> 23:12.820
I've only brought ruin on myself.

23:32.200 --> 23:33.250
I never expected

23:33.640 --> 23:34.860
you to manage

23:34.880 --> 23:37.210
to bring him back unharmed.

23:37.960 --> 23:41.180
Qingqiu truly holds wondrous powers.

23:43.790 --> 23:45.970
Qingqiu breeds extraordinary souls.

23:46.550 --> 23:47.580
No wonder my senior brother

23:47.600 --> 23:48.970
is such a peerless,

23:48.990 --> 23:49.900
elegant genius.

23:50.200 --> 23:51.250
Do you agree, Mr. Hu?

23:52.680 --> 23:53.420
Well said.

23:54.160 --> 23:55.620
So you do know my senior brother.

23:56.880 --> 23:58.380
Where is he?

24:00.310 --> 24:01.770
How would I know?

24:02.310 --> 24:03.690
With thousands of disciples at Wuyue Court,

24:03.840 --> 24:05.450
there is no way to tell him from the rest.

24:05.680 --> 24:07.380
What court? Wuyue Court.

24:09.710 --> 24:12.860
Give up hope. You'll never find him.

24:24.790 --> 24:26.770
Tongzhou, what does this line mean?

24:28.310 --> 24:28.900
This one?

24:30.710 --> 24:33.100
When the heart is unpurified, desires must be cast away.

24:34.680 --> 24:35.210
Like this.

24:36.750 --> 24:38.900
It means you must cast aside distracting thoughts.

24:39.440 --> 24:40.820
While cultivating qi,

24:40.840 --> 24:42.620
focus your mind on your breath

24:42.880 --> 24:43.820
and banish all stray thoughts.

24:43.990 --> 24:44.820
Only then will you make progress.

24:48.710 --> 24:50.180
Once you fully grasp the practice,

24:50.470 --> 24:51.580
even without controlling your breath,

24:51.840 --> 24:54.340
the vital qi will naturally fill your dantian.

24:57.400 --> 24:58.730
You'll make it. I believe in you.

25:03.750 --> 25:04.420
Sit down.

25:10.510 --> 25:13.250
Speak. What happened at Xingzheng  Hall?

25:14.030 --> 25:16.140
Why do you avoid Xiuyuan as if he were a plague?

25:17.640 --> 25:19.900
Nothing much. We've parted ways.

25:20.270 --> 25:21.420
We won't stay together from now on.

25:21.840 --> 25:23.050
You claim it's nothing?

25:23.510 --> 25:24.770
You once swore to live and die together.

25:24.790 --> 25:25.970
Can't just split up so easily.

25:28.960 --> 25:31.820
Once we graduate, we'll go our separate ways.

25:32.680 --> 25:33.900
With so many immortal sects,

25:34.960 --> 25:36.340
Tongzhou will head to Xingzheng Hall,

25:37.270 --> 25:38.380
and I to Wuyue Court.

25:39.470 --> 25:40.620
As for Lei Xiuyuan,

25:42.310 --> 25:43.380
he can go wherever he pleases.

25:43.960 --> 25:44.940
We're bound to part sooner or later.

25:44.990 --> 25:46.010
Better split early than drag it out.

25:46.990 --> 25:49.100
Better split early?

25:53.160 --> 25:55.620
Lifei, why must you go to Wuyue Court?

25:56.920 --> 25:58.580
There are clues about my master.

25:59.470 --> 26:02.010
Besides, Qin and Yue, who visited last time,

26:02.160 --> 26:03.100
seemed really kind.

26:05.640 --> 26:08.010
I feel like you're hiding something from me.

26:09.710 --> 26:11.530
Quit talking about me. What about you?

26:11.840 --> 26:13.050
Where will you and Changyue go?

26:16.990 --> 26:18.100
I don't know.

26:26.470 --> 26:28.420
I'm inferior to Ye in sword skills

26:28.790 --> 26:30.250
and to Changyue in spirit art.

26:32.960 --> 26:34.860
I'm afraid we'll take separate paths.

26:36.340 --> 26:37.660
Don't sell yourself short.

26:39.030 --> 26:40.900
I heard you learned artifact crafting under Mr. Mo.

26:40.920 --> 26:41.730
That's a fine skill.

26:42.750 --> 26:44.180
I've only picked up the basics.

26:44.710 --> 26:46.210
There's a long journey ahead.

26:46.440 --> 26:48.290
Exactly, the future stretches far.

26:48.310 --> 26:49.660
Leave future matters for later.

26:50.470 --> 26:53.010
For now, push all worries aside,

26:53.270 --> 26:53.970
study hard,

26:54.070 --> 26:55.860
and strive to enter our dream immortal sects soon.

26:56.030 --> 26:56.530
Okay.

26:57.400 --> 26:57.940
Okay.

27:03.510 --> 27:04.690
When you suddenly headed to Xingzheng Hall,

27:05.270 --> 27:07.620
I guessed it was about Lu.

27:08.600 --> 27:12.140
Years ago, my mother sent him to protect you.

27:14.990 --> 27:15.770
Is

27:16.440 --> 27:18.050
he gone?

27:19.510 --> 27:20.770
I dragged him into this mess.

27:23.510 --> 27:26.450
I'm unforgivable.

27:27.400 --> 27:29.730
Don't blame yourself harshly, Xiuyuan.

27:30.920 --> 27:33.490
I don't know the full story,

27:34.160 --> 27:36.730
but his soul above would

27:36.750 --> 27:37.940
definitely want you to be alright.

27:39.030 --> 27:39.940
The departed are at peace.

27:41.640 --> 27:44.100
What will you do next?

27:45.310 --> 27:46.180
Make amends.

27:49.750 --> 27:50.730
Avenge Shanhua.

27:51.310 --> 27:51.970
Avenge?

27:52.710 --> 27:53.770
Who's the culprit?

27:54.550 --> 27:56.180
Xingzheng Hall or Longming Sanctuary?

27:57.400 --> 27:58.290
You don't need to know.

27:59.710 --> 28:00.250
I…

28:01.510 --> 28:03.530
Xiuyuan, Xiuyuan,

28:04.640 --> 28:05.420
most things

28:05.880 --> 28:07.340
in life are beyond our control.

28:08.680 --> 28:09.770
Now that mistakes have been made,

28:10.550 --> 28:13.010
time will eventually heal all rifts.

28:14.270 --> 28:15.010
Take us, for example.

28:15.990 --> 28:17.940
Back then,

28:17.960 --> 28:19.140
I could've stopped everything,

28:19.550 --> 28:21.210
yet I let you take my place to face death.

28:21.920 --> 28:22.940
I was wrong, too.

28:23.600 --> 28:24.340
But now,

28:26.440 --> 28:27.940
we can still sit here

28:29.100 --> 28:30.180
and talk calmly together.

28:34.790 --> 28:38.940
By the way, Lifei will join Wuyue Court.

28:41.200 --> 28:42.010
Wuyue Court?

29:02.070 --> 29:02.970
What are you doing here?

29:05.710 --> 29:06.690
I'll help you join Wuyue Court.

29:09.400 --> 29:09.970
No need.

29:14.580 --> 29:15.210
I've looked into it.

29:16.510 --> 29:17.730
There are only two ways to join Wuyue Court.

29:18.270 --> 29:19.770
First, get recommended by an inner disciple

29:19.790 --> 29:20.530
to join the outer sect.

29:20.990 --> 29:22.140
Second, pass the academy assessment

29:22.550 --> 29:23.380
and gain an elder's approval

29:23.600 --> 29:24.180
to join the inner sect.

29:25.310 --> 29:27.050
But Wuyue Court hasn't recruited

29:27.070 --> 29:28.290
any inner disciples for over a decade.

29:29.310 --> 29:29.940
So?

29:31.310 --> 29:32.250
So I want to help you.

29:32.960 --> 29:34.340
More hands mean better odds.

29:35.790 --> 29:37.210
Is having someone who betrayed me

29:39.640 --> 29:41.660
an advantage or a burden?

29:43.120 --> 29:44.010
I will never fail you again.

29:48.030 --> 29:48.730
That's your own promise.

29:49.680 --> 29:50.420
Stop following me.

29:56.220 --> 29:57.010
I won't let go.

29:58.380 --> 29:59.180
Wherever you go,

30:01.180 --> 30:02.010
I'll find you.

30:08.980 --> 30:10.010
You're only relying on this, right?

30:12.700 --> 30:13.970
You think the Fragrance Bond ties us together,

30:14.990 --> 30:16.050
leaving a chance between us.

30:22.230 --> 30:23.420
I'll break it right now.

30:36.660 --> 30:37.530
Let go.

31:10.460 --> 31:11.340
Must you break it?

31:18.790 --> 31:19.290
Yes.

31:32.030 --> 31:32.770
Don't hurt yourself.

31:36.030 --> 31:37.340
I'll go with you to see Mr. Mo.

31:53.470 --> 31:53.970
Wait.

31:56.940 --> 31:57.580
Come with me now.

31:57.710 --> 31:58.380
Or else,

31:58.660 --> 31:59.620
don't blame me for being rude.

32:01.070 --> 32:01.730
Ms. Lin?

32:20.460 --> 32:21.530
Where did you get this demonic artifact?

32:33.400 --> 32:35.480
[Shen Jiao, Wanxian Sect]

32:43.860 --> 32:44.860
Who exactly are you?

33:09.860 --> 33:11.730
This is a horn of Yecha!

33:12.220 --> 33:13.490
Horn of Yecha?

33:16.270 --> 33:18.210
The Demon Lord Yecha from the storybook?

33:19.180 --> 33:19.730
Exactly.

33:20.070 --> 33:21.340
During the Sea Calamity battle,

33:21.710 --> 33:23.180
the Demon Lord's two horns were chopped off.

33:23.790 --> 33:26.210
Mr. Shen of the Wanxian Sect in the East Sea took one.

33:26.710 --> 33:27.900
With its demonic energy,

33:28.220 --> 33:29.050
it can command spirits.

33:29.710 --> 33:34.620
Word has it that Mr. Shen crafted it into an ornament

33:35.310 --> 33:37.210
to protect his beloved daughter Jiao.

33:38.860 --> 33:40.900
Jiao, why are you

33:41.380 --> 33:42.340
here in disguise?

33:43.230 --> 33:43.860
Right.

33:44.220 --> 33:45.340
I'm Shen Jiao.

33:47.470 --> 33:48.100
You monster!

33:48.660 --> 33:49.620
Where is the real Lin You?

33:50.270 --> 33:51.450
Since you call me a monster,

33:51.700 --> 33:53.140
she's locked deep in my monster lair

33:53.620 --> 33:55.140
and tormented, wanting to live yet cannot,

33:55.180 --> 33:56.010
wanting to die yet cannot.

33:59.470 --> 33:59.970
Jiao,

34:00.550 --> 34:01.140
don't talk nonsense.

34:02.220 --> 34:03.420
You'd never do such cruel things.

34:03.460 --> 34:04.730
Why utter such vicious words?

34:04.860 --> 34:05.860
Do you think one kiss

34:06.270 --> 34:07.050
means you truly know me?

34:15.990 --> 34:16.610
Yanfan,

34:17.470 --> 34:19.900
escort Jiao to the Disciplinary Pavilion.

34:20.380 --> 34:21.340
We'll deal with her properly

34:22.030 --> 34:22.860
once we find Lin You.

34:24.780 --> 34:25.300
Understood.

34:37.300 --> 34:37.970
Xiuyuan,

34:38.820 --> 34:39.610
step forward.

35:11.630 --> 35:13.970
You've overcome countless hardships to get here.

35:14.720 --> 35:16.300
Even if your loved one is gone,

35:16.630 --> 35:18.530
you must cherish your own life.

35:19.150 --> 35:22.300
When tough troubles arise later,

35:22.860 --> 35:25.940
there'll always be room to turn things around.

35:27.990 --> 35:29.010
Thank you for your guidance.

35:31.240 --> 35:31.820
Mr. Zuo,

35:34.150 --> 35:35.170
Jiao is crafty.

35:35.190 --> 35:36.570
I fear Mr. Mo may be soft-hearted.

35:36.940 --> 35:37.740
I want to check on them.

35:40.240 --> 35:40.820
Go ahead.

35:59.070 --> 36:00.260
You'll have to wait here for now.

36:00.820 --> 36:02.090
[Disciplinary Pavilion]
I'll explain everything to Mr. Zuo.

36:02.510 --> 36:03.340
Because of me, you…

36:03.380 --> 36:04.650
Quit chattering.

36:05.070 --> 36:06.340
Either go back to the East Sea with me

36:06.380 --> 36:07.050
and marry me,

36:07.470 --> 36:08.220
or get lost right now.

36:09.470 --> 36:10.940
One minute you push him to marry you,

36:11.190 --> 36:12.420
and the next you tell him to get lost.

36:13.460 --> 36:14.340
What do you want?

36:14.980 --> 36:15.970
None of your business.

36:16.380 --> 36:17.940
If you two hadn't ruined my plan,

36:18.240 --> 36:19.260
I wouldn't have been locked up here.

36:19.780 --> 36:21.010
You messed up my plan, okay?

36:26.030 --> 36:26.610
Mr. Mo,

36:28.590 --> 36:29.610
I want to break the Fragrance Bond.

36:33.900 --> 36:34.530
He agreed too.

36:38.070 --> 36:39.420
One moment, your hearts align,

36:39.550 --> 36:40.650
and the next, you turn cold to him.

36:41.550 --> 36:42.490
I'd like to ask you.

36:42.780 --> 36:43.820
What do you want?

36:48.900 --> 36:49.530
That's how life works.

36:50.300 --> 36:51.530
Pick things up and let them go when needed.

36:52.720 --> 36:54.340
Far better than someone clinging on relentlessly.

36:57.070 --> 36:57.970
Letting go?

36:58.550 --> 36:59.860
That's just an excuse for cold, faithless folks

36:59.900 --> 37:01.380
to seduce and abandon others.

37:04.900 --> 37:05.780
Is that not the truth?

37:09.820 --> 37:11.490
You said Mr. Mo betrayed you.

37:12.300 --> 37:13.380
Were you two ever together?

37:13.980 --> 37:14.530
We were.

37:20.940 --> 37:21.860
Three years ago,

37:22.460 --> 37:23.940
I found cultivation in the East Sea dull,

37:24.510 --> 37:25.780
so I headed to Mount Que alone,

37:26.300 --> 37:27.650
hoping to catch a spirit as my pet.

37:28.300 --> 37:29.490
Yet I accidentally got poisoned by a monster

37:29.990 --> 37:30.900
and nearly lost my life.

37:45.550 --> 37:46.260
At that moment,

37:46.990 --> 37:48.650
I knew what love at first sight meant.

37:49.470 --> 37:51.570
Women of the East Sea are bold and free-spirited.

37:52.460 --> 37:53.300
If we fancy someone,

37:53.630 --> 37:54.650
we'll pursue them without hesitation.

38:13.860 --> 38:15.260
I thought my sincere devotion

38:15.300 --> 38:16.130
would win mutual affection.

38:16.980 --> 38:18.340
Yet the very next day,

38:18.380 --> 38:19.420
he left a letter and vanished,

38:20.030 --> 38:21.860
telling me he'd report to his mater at Xingzheng Hall,

38:21.900 --> 38:22.610
and then answer me.

38:23.420 --> 38:24.220
But once he left,

38:24.720 --> 38:25.820
I never heard from him again,

38:26.550 --> 38:27.900
so I had to seek him out at Xingzheng Hall.

38:44.380 --> 38:44.970
Later,

38:45.380 --> 38:46.860
I found out he'd left the hall

38:47.300 --> 38:48.420
and hidden in Chufeng Academy.

38:48.980 --> 38:50.170
That's why I kidnapped Lin You

38:50.550 --> 38:52.490
and snuck into the academy by disguising myself as her.

38:58.340 --> 38:58.940
Jiao,

39:01.510 --> 39:02.530
I've let you down.

39:04.940 --> 39:06.380
Just pretend we never crossed paths.

39:07.340 --> 39:08.450
Why chase after me still?

39:08.900 --> 39:10.740
So you did seduce and abandon her.

39:16.670 --> 39:17.300
Mo Yanfan,

39:17.860 --> 39:18.490
you avoided me,

39:18.510 --> 39:19.740
fearing your master Xuanshanzi

39:19.780 --> 39:20.860
would slay me in rage.

39:21.340 --> 39:22.010
Let me tell you,

39:22.030 --> 39:22.650
I fear nothing.

39:23.030 --> 39:24.340
I know you had your reasons.

39:24.630 --> 39:25.490
But I'm no delicate young lady

39:25.510 --> 39:26.900
who fades at the slightest wind.

39:27.240 --> 39:28.900
Since I hold affection for you,

39:29.190 --> 39:30.220
as long as I'm alive,

39:30.720 --> 39:31.970
I'll never let go of you

39:32.190 --> 39:33.420
for the rest of my life.

39:36.980 --> 39:38.170
Why torture yourself?

39:38.630 --> 39:39.700
I bear all hardship willingly,

39:40.670 --> 39:41.820
and I'll not regret it.

39:52.780 --> 39:53.420
Jiao,

39:53.920 --> 39:55.900
Mr. Zuo has sent a letter to the Wanxian Sect.

39:57.440 --> 39:59.820
Mr. Shen will arrive any day now.

40:00.190 --> 40:01.570
Even if he comes, it'll change nothing.

40:01.880 --> 40:03.170
I will not back down or let go.

40:08.840 --> 40:09.420
I'm tired

40:09.760 --> 40:10.780
and done talking to all of you.

40:11.400 --> 40:12.570
Get out of my sight

40:13.220 --> 40:13.820
and leave me alone.

40:28.150 --> 40:29.780
Do you really want to break the Fragrance Bond?

40:31.470 --> 40:33.050
If you find that it troubles you,

40:33.800 --> 40:34.900
we may come back in a few days.

40:39.550 --> 40:41.010
My mind is all in chaos today,

40:41.880 --> 40:42.570
and I have no will to work on it.

40:45.280 --> 40:46.780
Besides, you three must come

40:46.880 --> 40:48.220
together to break the Fragrance Bond.

40:48.800 --> 40:49.340
Lifei.

40:54.030 --> 40:54.650
Tongzhou.

40:54.800 --> 40:55.420
Lifei,

40:55.800 --> 40:57.420
I just sensed the Fragrance Bond stir.

40:57.760 --> 40:58.340
Are you alright?

41:00.190 --> 41:00.700
I'm fine.

41:04.470 --> 41:05.010
Mr. Mo,

41:05.800 --> 41:06.860
we shall take our leave.

41:14.400 --> 41:14.900
Let's go.

41:18.150 --> 41:18.700
Are you really alright?

41:18.880 --> 41:19.610
Yes.

41:20.220 --> 41:20.820
Glad to hear that.

42:13.470 --> 42:15.260
Why do I keep dreaming of the Demon Lord Yecha?

42:17.030 --> 42:17.860
Is that demonic energy

42:19.030 --> 42:20.220
related to me?

42:42.200 --> 42:42.510
[The Eternal Fragrance]

42:42.510 --> 42:44.720
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

42:57.500 --> 43:01.020
♪The warmth within my arms♪

43:01.180 --> 43:04.700
♪I can no longer hold on to♪

43:04.820 --> 43:08.340
♪In the cold night, how can I♪

43:08.460 --> 43:11.940
♪Keep you warm until sunrise?♪

43:11.940 --> 43:15.580
♪My heartbeat freezes♪

43:15.980 --> 43:19.260
♪I can no longer tell you♪

43:19.380 --> 43:22.900
♪Looking you in the eyes, I cannot♪

43:22.940 --> 43:25.940
♪Utter that line♪

43:26.100 --> 43:28.140
♪Knowing love and hate♪

43:28.220 --> 43:32.620
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

43:33.340 --> 43:35.420
♪I still linger on♪

43:35.580 --> 43:39.860
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

43:40.020 --> 43:44.540
♪Last night's stars cast faint glimmers♪

43:44.620 --> 43:48.140
♪But we thought nothing of it♪

43:48.220 --> 43:51.660
♪With a heartbroken cry♪

43:51.940 --> 43:55.180
♪I wish you well♪

43:55.340 --> 43:57.060
♪Knowing right and wrong♪

43:57.220 --> 44:01.900
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

44:02.500 --> 44:04.580
♪You're still screaming♪

44:04.740 --> 44:09.220
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

44:09.340 --> 44:13.820
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stand in its way♪

44:14.060 --> 44:17.020
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

44:17.140 --> 44:19.020
♪Leaping straight into♪

44:19.140 --> 44:23.900
♪That heartbreaking past♪

44:24.140 --> 44:27.660
♪Just to keep you safe♪

44:34.100 --> 44:37.420
♪My breath is about to stop♪

44:37.540 --> 44:41.060
♪Those hands can no longer hold yours♪

44:41.180 --> 44:44.620
♪Through the future snow, wind, and fog♪

44:44.780 --> 44:47.980
♪Who will be there by your side?♪

44:48.100 --> 44:51.820
♪I smile as it ends♪

44:51.980 --> 44:55.620
♪Afraid that you might cry for me♪

44:55.820 --> 44:59.220
♪Quietly, I turn into a sky lantern♪

44:59.380 --> 45:02.500
♪To light your way through the night♪

45:02.580 --> 45:04.620
♪Knowing love and hate♪

45:04.700 --> 45:09.100
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

45:09.860 --> 45:11.900
♪I still linger on♪

45:12.060 --> 45:16.340
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

45:16.500 --> 45:21.020
♪The storm looms, yet I stand in its way♪

45:21.100 --> 45:24.300
♪Torn inside, still I burn bright♪

45:24.500 --> 45:26.460
♪With the light from my fingertips♪

45:26.540 --> 45:30.940
♪I build a paradise♪

45:31.100 --> 45:34.580
♪To wander with you♪
